# Exclude locally-extracted map files from Vercel deployment.
# The maps folder contains ~400 files (~1.9 GB) extracted locally
# but only 1 file is committed to git. Vercel CLI would upload all
# local files — use this to prevent the 1.9 GB upload.
# Token images (creatures/assets) are small enough (~47 MB) and stay included.
public/tokens/maps/
